{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/Base.html#Real.induction_Ico_mul\"><span class=\"name\">Real</span>.<span class=\"name\">induction_Ico_mul</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">P</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x₀ </span><span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hr</span> : <span class=\"fn\">1</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\">r</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hx₀</span> : <span class=\"fn\">0</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\">x₀</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">base</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ <span class=\"fn\">x</span> ∈ <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Interval/Set/Defs.html#Set.Ico\">Set.Ico</a> <span class=\"fn\">x₀</span> (<span class=\"fn\">r</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">x₀</span>)</span>, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">P</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">step</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ <span class=\"fn\">n</span> ≥ <span class=\"fn\">1</span>, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(∀ <span class=\"fn\">z</span> ∈ <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Interval/Set/Defs.html#Set.Ico\">Set.Ico</a> <span class=\"fn\">x₀</span> (<span class=\"fn\">r</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HPow.hPow\">^</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">x₀</span>)</span>, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">P</span> <span class=\"fn\">z</span></span>)</span> → <span class=\"fn\">∀ <span class=\"fn\">z</span> ∈ <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Interval/Set/Defs.html#Set.Ico\">Set.Ico</a> (<span class=\"fn\">r</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HPow.hPow\">^</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">x₀</span>) (<span class=\"fn\">r</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HPow.hPow\">^</a> (<span class=\"fn\">n</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAdd.hAdd\">+</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span>) <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">x₀</span>)</span>, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">P</span> <span class=\"fn\">z</span></span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#GE.ge\">≥</a> <span class=\"fn\">x₀</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">P</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Induction principle for intervals of real numbers: if a proposition `P` is true\non `[x₀, r * x₀)` and if `P` for `[x₀, r^n * x₀)` implies `P` for `[r^n * x₀, r^(n+1) * x₀)`,\nthen `P` is true for all `x ≥ x₀`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/Base.html#Real.induction_Ico_mul","kind":"theorem","line":611,"name":"Real.induction_Ico_mul","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/Base.lean#L611-L630"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_k